height="583"
srcset="https://katomelon.github.io/blog/blog/p/intro-to-ai-w3/image/image_qtOtKSEPF1_hu_37892f4b588ff198.png 480w, https://katomelon.github.io/blog/blog/p/intro-to-ai-w3/image/image_qtOtKSEPF1_hu_49fed75410e48c91.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="207"
data-flex-basis="498px"
>&lt;br />CPU适用于复杂逻辑控制，例如武器装备，IT等场景；GPU适用于密码学、挖矿、图形计算等需要平行计算的场景。CPU耗能小，GPU耗能高。&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
